gomodel:SYNGO_1494  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Synaptosomes of Amphiphysin knockout mice display reduced recycling of synaptic vesicles (Fig. 4 C,D). Cortical neurons in culture show also defects in synaptic vesicle dynamics as revealed by FM1-43 dye studies.\n\n13/10/2017 Pim\n- Endocytosis of SVs is measured by quanitfying uptake of FM1-43 upon stimulation of synaptosomes.. Experimental description: \"Decreased Synaptic Vesicle Recycling Efficiency and Cognitive Deficits in Amphiphysin 1 Knockout Mice\". p. 789 (title)" ;
